            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>paprika chicken </strong>to the tray[s] with the onion and tomato and drizzle everything with <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and put the tray[s] in the oven for 18-20 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the vegetables have softened</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1677698746118-x200.jpg",
