    {
      "instruction": "<p>Place the<strong> salad </strong>on a plate and top with the <strong>crispy potatoes</strong>, <strong>roasted onion </strong>and<strong> tomato</strong>,<strong> sliced paprika chicken </strong>and <strong>charred pepper </strong>– this is your<strong> Spanish-style chicken breast & charred pepper salad</strong></p><p>Drizzle the <strong>spicy aioli </strong>all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
